snippet.title: Age of Survival Official Steam Trailer (Revision #1)
snippet.description:
New official Steam Trailer for Age of Survival (1st revision). Much more to come in the second revision, including animals, and ocean exploration.

Age of Survival coming soon on Steam, Aug 25th 2015
